import logo from './logo.svg';
import './App.css';

function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Fragment>
        <AuthProvider>
          <Routes>
            <Route path="/" element={<HomePage />} />
            <Route path="/profile" element={<Profile />} />
            <Route path="/jobs" element={<JobBoard searchedWord={searchedWord} handleChangeWord={handleChangeWord} filterItems={filterItems} />} />
            <Route path="/messages" element={<Messages1 />} />
            <Route path="/proposals" element={<Proposals searchedWord={searchedWord} handleChangeWord={handleChangeWord} filterItems={filterItems}/>} />
            <Route path="/showapplications" element={<ShowCandidatesMobile />} />
            <Route path="/showcandidates/:id" element={<ShowCandidates />} />
            <Route path="/createProposal" element={<CreateProposal />} />
            <Route path="/createJob" element={<CreateJob />} />
            <Route path="/workers" element={<WorkerBoard searchedWord={searchedWord} handleChangeWord={handleChangeWord} filterItems={filterItems} />} />
            <Route path="/workers/:id" element={<WorkerProfile />} />
            <Route path="/login" element={<Login />} />
            <Route path="/register" element={<Register />} />
            <Route path="/jobsbusiness" element={<JobsBusiness />} />
            <Route path="*" element={<Navigate to="/" />} />
          </Routes>
        </AuthProvider>
      </Fragment>
    </BrowserRouter>
  );
}

export default App;
